==Personal life==
Colombo met librarian Jasper Badcock (born 1962) in 1989, shortly after Aretha had founded Aretha's Gifts. They married a year later and had three children together: 
* [[Dwight Colombo|Dwight]] (born 1990) - United States Air Force officer and accountant 
* [[Andrew Colombo|Andrew]] (born 1992) - Reporter for Dominion Broadcasting Service
* [[Ellie Colombo|Ellie]] (born 1994) - Exotic dancer at The Axis Club

==Death==
On May 22, 2024, Colombo suffered a massive heart attack in her home. She was rushed to the hospital, where she was later pronounced dead at the age of 58. She is survived by her husband, three children, two sisters, and granddaughter. 

